items.text: full on middle stump, tapped off the front foot to midwicket, nice and early call for the run. Better rotation of the strike, now, between these two
items.shortText: Rubel Hossain to Sikandar Raza, 1 run

items.text: loses his balance while swaying away! Short on middle, and once again coming to the batsman near his chest, does very well to get out of the line of the ball, but falls over while trying to get away
items.shortText: Rubel Hossain to Waller, no run

items.text: too short outside off, flies off the surface this time, and it's too high for the keeper as well. Free runs
items.shortText: Rubel Hossain to Waller, 5 wides

items.text: full outside off, and it's crunched! Driven beautifully past cover, and there's no stopping that. Hammered!
items.shortText: Rubel Hossain to Waller, FOUR runs

items.text: full and straight on off stump, hit back to mid off off the front foot
items.shortText: Rubel Hossain to Waller, no run

items.text: full on middle stump, turned off his toes to midwicket with soft hands, forces the keeper to chase behind it and they scamper through for the single
items.shortText: Sunzamul Islam to Sikandar Raza, 1 run

items.text: full on off stump, hit hard back to Sunzamul. Puts his hands out, but dropped! Just couldn't hold on to it
items.shortText: Sunzamul Islam to Waller, no run

items.text: full outside off, carved inside out to cover
items.shortText: Sunzamul Islam to Waller, no run

items.text: makes amends! Floats another one on off stump, too close to cut once again, and it's edged through to Sabbir at first slip. Sharp, sharp catch. Taken low to his right
items.shortText: Sunzamul Islam to Waller, OUT

dismissal.text: MN Waller c Sabbir Rahman b Sunzamul Islam 13 (30b 1x4 0x6) SR: 43.33

items.preText: Peter Moor, right-hand bat. Needs to do better than the average of 17 that he has in ODIs.
items.text: full outside off, big stride forward and defended
items.shortText: Sunzamul Islam to Moor, no run

items.text: full on off stump once again, defended off the front foot with soft hands. Carefully played, with eyes on the ball at all times
items.shortText: Sunzamul Islam to Moor, no run

items.text: short and wide outside off, slapped over point on this occasion. Well hit, and races away to the boundary. Latches onto the width
items.shortText: Rubel Hossain to Sikandar Raza, FOUR runs

items.preText: Outkast: "Four words for Zimbabwe - "Bring Back Vusi Sibanda!!!""
items.text: good length outside off, angling in, shoulders his arms after covering his off stump, stays low as it goes through to the keeper
items.shortText: Rubel Hossain to Sikandar Raza, no run

items.text: back of a length outside off, extra bounce through to Raza, worked off his hips to midwicket off the back foot. They walk through for the run
items.shortText: Rubel Hossain to Sikandar Raza, 1 run

items.text: full outside off, goes straight through to Mushfiq with the batsman offering no shot. Came forward and covered his off-stump line though
items.shortText: Rubel Hossain to Moor, no run

items.text: back of a length outside off, punched off the front foot with the bat's open face. Can't  go past cover point
items.shortText: Rubel Hossain to Moor, no run

items.text: good length outside off, tapped off the front foot to cover
items.shortText: Rubel Hossain to Moor, no run

items.text: tossed up full on off stump, almost a yorker. Dug away back past the non-striker
items.shortText: Sunzamul Islam to Sikandar Raza, no run

items.text: good length on off stump, backs away and muscles this past Sunzamul's right. Through to long off
items.shortText: Sunzamul Islam to Sikandar Raza, 1 run

items.text: tossed up outside off stump, driven to short extra cover
items.shortText: Sunzamul Islam to Moor, no run

items.text: full on off stump, pushed through to long off after stepping forward
items.shortText: Sunzamul Islam to Moor, 1 run

items.text: quicker ball this time, good length on middle and leg, cramps the batsman as he nudges this to square leg
items.shortText: Sunzamul Islam to Sikandar Raza, no run

items.text: full on middle and leg, down on one knee as Raza tries to sweep. Goes down the leg side, however
items.shortText: Sunzamul Islam to Sikandar Raza, 1 wide

items.text: full outside off, tries to drive with the turn, comes off the inside of the bat instead. Trickles back to the bowler
items.shortText: Sunzamul Islam to Sikandar Raza, no run

items.preText: Shakib's back. Two for 18 off his first five overs
items.text: tossed up on middle stump, prods forward and defends with soft hands
items.shortText: Shakib Al Hasan to Moor, no run
